pageContext.claim: “Elijah Cummings spends all of his time trying to hurt innocent people through “Oversight.” He does NOTHING for his very poor, very dangerous and very badly run district! Take a look.... #BlacksForTrump2020”
pageContext.analysis: Cummings's district includes rural and suburban parts of Baltimore and Howard counties, as well as parts of Baltimore city. These include some of the lowest crime and highest-income ZIP codes in the country. Cummings won his last reelection with nearly 80 percent of the vote.
